Requires:         R-grid 
Requires:         R-CRAN-gplots 

%description
For multiple ranked input lists (full or partial) representing the same
set of N objects, the package TopKLists offers (1) statistical inference
on the lengths of informative top-k lists, (2) stochastic aggregation of
full or partial lists, and (3) graphical tools for the statistical
exploration of input lists, and for the visualization of aggregation
results.

